data.description: Like new construction, this home boasts so many great features it's sure to make a short day of showings. Large open floor plan with modern kitchen, tons of storage cabinets and beautiful countertops, and new backsplash. Located conveniently to bases, downtown Norfolk, and Greenbriar. Massive backyard on a corner lot, fully fenced in, with patio, fire pit, vegetable garden and rain water retention system. Large bedrooms have ample closet space, and full garage perfect for vehicles or additional storage. 19 panel Solar array installed conveys and transferable with $110/mo payments, increasing to $151/mo in Nov. Security system conveys. VA assumable loan at 2.625% interest! Don't miss out on this opportunity, Call to schedule your showing today!
